Detailed Description

Request for a specific stored route.

After the normal RequestPacket header the request packet contains: {tabular}{lll} Pos & Size & Destription \ REQUEST_HEADER_SIZE & 4 bytes & routeID \ +4 & 4 bytes & createTime \ {tabular}
